In addition, many videos have already been posted on the network presenting the operational areas in Iraq and Afghanistan that were carried out in real mission, but the British army has only recently packed for the loading of these videos.
The Americans do the recruitment a little differently by using the American's Army shooting game for free. In this game, the player can put himself directly in the position of soldiers within a more or less real simulation.
